00:17:52,970 --> 00:17:54,514
- Bukan.
- Dia Yu Jae-seok?

227
00:17:54,514 --> 00:17:57,016
- Kau bukan Yu Jae-seok?
- Lalu dia siapa?

228
00:17:58,810 --> 00:18:01,312
Putra Tn. Kim yang mengelola
