229
00:18:01,312 --> 00:18:03,481
Kau Dong-gu. Benar?

230
00:18:03,481 --> 00:18:04,774
Ya, Dong-gu...

231
00:18:04,774 --> 00:18:07,652
- Dia Dong-gu.
